      "span_text": "PARP-proficient (PARP ϩ / ϩ ) and PARP-deficient (PARP Ϫ / Ϫ ) mice generated by [CITATION_1] were sacrified by an overdose of CO 2 and 10 ml of RPMI 1640 medium was injected IP."
